data.description: WOW! This beautiful turn key home sitting on a spectacularly landscaped back yard with over 1+ acres. This property conveniently placed near the boarder of Fairfax and located in Montyville Estates which is minutes within everything you could need and it comes without the restrictions of an HOA. Enjoy the spectacular open floor layout with all stainless steel kitchen appliances throughout with a generous amount of counter space. This home features four bedrooms with three and a half baths with a finished basement including a built in bar perfect for hosting guests. Get cozy and warm in the colder seasons while sitting next to the fire place or kick back in the sunroom to catch some rays in the warmer seasons. You can even enjoy a nice movie night down in the basements movie room. Sit back and enjoy the scenic pond waterfall flow into the beautiful koi pond.
